'''亞當·拉哈姆迪'''（{{bd|1995年|4月22日}}）出生於[[魁北克|魁北克]][[魁北克市|魁北克市]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://m.sochi2014.com/en/athlete-adam-lamhamedi |title=Sochi 2014 profile |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2014-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309052327/http://m.sochi2014.com/en/athlete-adam-lamhamedi |dead-url=no }}</ref>，為摩洛哥籍加拿大高山滑雪運動員。2010年開始參加國際滑總的賽事<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://data.fis-ski.com/dynamic/athlete-biography.html?sector=AL&competitorid=172523 |title=Adam Lamhamedi FIS Biography |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2014-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201180930/http://data.fis-ski.com/dynamic/athlete-biography.html?sector=AL&competitorid=172523 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。拉哈姆迪出生於[[加拿大|加拿大]]，<ref name="a">{{cite news |last= |first= |date=14 January 2014 |title=Ski olympique à saveur marocaine |url=http://www.radio-canada.ca/emissions/medium_large/2011-2012/chronique.asp?idChronique=325140 |newspaper=[[Radio_Canada|Radio Canada]] |location= |publisher= |accessdate= 17 January 2014|language=fr}}</ref>然後取得參賽資格代表摩洛哥參加在[[索契|索契]]舉行的[[2014年冬季奧運|2014年冬季奧運]]。<ref name="a"/>

雖然拉哈姆迪在加拿大出生，不過他的父親來自摩洛哥這才讓他有為摩洛哥出賽的機會。<ref name="a"/>拉哈姆迪奪得冬季青年奧林匹克運動首個超級大曲道賽事的金牌，並成為第一位奪得冬季青年奧運項目獎牌的非洲國家運動員。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.olympic.org/news/yog-champion-adam-lamhamedi-gets-set-to-represent-morocco-at-sochi-2014/199714 |title=YOG champion Adam Lamhamedi gets set to represent Morocco at Sochi 2014 |last1= |first1= |last2= |first2= |date=23 May 2013 |website=www.olympic.org |publisher=[[International_Olympic_Committee|International Olympic Committee]] |accessdate=7 January 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309082748/http://www.olympic.org/news/yog-champion-adam-lamhamedi-gets-set-to-represent-morocco-at-sochi-2014/199714 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

